    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《烽沙》是一款以中国古代为背景，融合建造、经营与战术策略的古代<strong>战争模拟建造游戏</strong>。玩家将从零开始，建设并经营兼具生产、防御与军事功能的古代兵垒。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏融合自由布局的建筑系统、以伍为单位的人口管理、动态四季与天气变化、以及深受诸子百家思潮影响的多样门客和强力效果。在敌军的入侵威胁下，除了经营与建造，你还需要构建防御工事、组织主动出击、开拓流民村庄，甚至通过祭祀与事件决策影响国运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于烽沙的玩法</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">===========================================================================================</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>1、“筑”——「高筑墙，广积粮，缓称王。」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——通过建造防御工事、发展农业和工业来夯实经济基础，应对天灾人祸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——拥有丰富的种植系统、建筑系统、采集系统、生产系统等，满足您的古代种田梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/20d2c0787b350e5f41cf0d5811f8901a.poster.avif?t=1770103662\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/20d2c0787b350e5f41cf0d5811f8901a.webm?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/20d2c0787b350e5f41cf0d5811f8901a.mp4?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2、“弈”——「百家争鸣，礼法并用。合纵连横，远交近攻。乱世之中，何以为道？」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——像城主诸侯一样，融合各派思想，制定外交策略，形成自己独特的治国理念和方针。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——百家争鸣的门客中可能就有像苏秦、张仪一样的纵横家，他们的技能将极大影响政策效果或外交效果，强调动态平衡与利益权衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/b2b0110c5f479d1ed7f4649a70ec79ef.poster.avif?t=1770103662\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/b2b0110c5f479d1ed7f4649a70ec79ef.webm?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/b2b0110c5f479d1ed7f4649a70ec79ef.mp4?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3、“伐”——「上兵伐谋。奇正相生。」 </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——不仅有常规的防御战或主动出征，还有更多像“战车兵”、“熊猫战士”、“魏武卒”这样的战争器械和奇兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——基于城墙和城防设施来规划战争建筑学，融合物理感强化系统，深刻体验古人 “物尽其用” 的实用主义战争观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/d464f8613c27e2921333be929b591521.poster.avif?t=1770103662\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/d464f8613c27e2921333be929b591521.webm?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/d464f8613c27e2921333be929b591521.mp4?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4、“祀”——「顺天时而耕战，应天命而祭祀。逆天而行，虽强必亡。」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>——祀天地以祷国运，祭祀系统影响各种天灾人祸和事件效果，如何应对和选择将会是对你道德的考验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——古语有云：福祸相依。在绝望的灾厄之后，往往也藏着发展的转机？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/5b473e8b2e30af4558592185ed36d15b.poster.avif?t=1770103662\" width=1170 height=630 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/5b473e8b2e30af4558592185ed36d15b.webm?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/5b473e8b2e30af4558592185ed36d15b.mp4?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>5、“革”---「治世不一道，便国不法古。不破不立，不变则衰。」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ——通过科技发展，建筑升级，物流体系等内容，不仅能体验到工具技术的进步，还能深刻感受到体制与文明的变革影响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——根据沙盒的形态和自有的资源，需要您不断调整当局的玩法，变法图强，鼎故革新。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/1ee0b992c023c26ae2bf77e8ff9191f1.poster.avif?t=1770103662\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/1ee0b992c023c26ae2bf77e8ff9191f1.webm?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733690/extras/1ee0b992c023c26ae2bf77e8ff9191f1.mp4?t=1770103662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特别说明：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当前的测试版本中不包括规划中的全部内容，欢迎加入Q群:1061507823 持续跟踪开发进度。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">===========================================================================================</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们知道，当前的版本内容与大家的期待相去甚远，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们也相信，一款真正完整的游戏，并非诞生于封闭的开发环境中，而是在与玩家持续不断的对话中共同打磨而成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >心怀敬畏，笃行致远，期待收到你的批评建议和反馈。</p>",
